				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">MK I + II is one of the MBC1-based collection carts, which use the MBC1 chip but with a different wiring. It's impossible to know this from the $0147 header, so an emulator (or a flash cart!) playing this game will fail if the cartridge is emulated with normal MBC1 logic.</div>

